    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Windows CI flaky failure:\n\n```\nFAILED   ...ld/Xtest_xdg_plugin/test/functional/plugin/pack_spec.lua:92: ...ld/Xtest_xdg_plugin/test/functional/plugin/pack_spec.lua @ 70: vim.pack get() opts.offline can fetch new updates\n...ld/Xtest_xdg_plugin/test/functional/plugin/pack_spec.lua:92: ...ld/Xtest_xdg_plugin/test/functional/plugin/pack_spec.lua:70: process still exists\nstack traceback:\n\ttest/functional/testnvim/exec_lua.lua:124: in function 'system_sync'\n\t...ld/Xtest_xdg_plugin/test/functional/plugin/pack_spec.lua:92: in function 'git_cmd'\n\t...ld/Xtest_xdg_plugin/test/functional/plugin/pack_spec.lua:104: in function 'init_test_repo'\n\t...ld/Xtest_xdg_plugin/test/functional/plugin/pack_spec.lua:2203: in function <...ld/Xtest_xdg_plugin/test/functional/plugin/pack_spec.lua:2201>\n```\n\ncc @echasnovski ",
